course_title: Adult/Gerontology Primary Care Nurse Practitioner Clinical Practicum I
course_description: This course will provide clinical practice experience with faculty oversight to develop skills in health assessment and physical exam, differential diagnosis, diagnostic reasoning and plan of care for common conditions.
prerequisites: NRSG 562D prerequisite and NRSG 565D co-requisite or equivalent transfer credit.
